page.title: 03The Dalston Show.
page.content: The Dalston Show is ususally held in August,this year it is on 10th August. This is a copy of the programme of events. 8.00am Showfield opens. 10.00am Judging of Horticultural and industrial section. 10.30am Judging of horse classes ring 2. 10.30am Judging dairy cattle 11.30am Judging beef cattle and calf dases 11.30am Hound trail (hounds) 12.10pm Hound trail (nonwinners) 12.30pm Jumping competitions coments ring 2 12.30pm Childs pet judging (ring 1) 12.30pm Cumberland & Westmorland wrestling. 1.10pm Hound trail (puppies) 1.40pm Hound trail (mixed madens) 2.00pm Grand Parade and presentations.
